@startuml
title UC-11 Create Course (Sequence)
participant Instructor
participant WebApp
participant CourseService
participant DB
participant NotificationService
participant Admin

Instructor -> WebApp: open Create Course -> submit draft or request review
WebApp -> CourseService: createCourse(payload, publish=false or pending)
CourseService -> DB: INSERT course (status draft/pending)
DB --> CourseService: courseId
alt requires approval
CourseService -> NotificationService: notifyAdmins(courseId)
NotificationService -> Admin: in-app/email
else auto-publish
CourseService -> DB: UPDATE course(status=published)
DB --> CourseService: published
CourseService -> NotificationService: notifyFollowers(course)
end
CourseService --> WebApp: ack
WebApp --> Instructor: show course saved/pending/published
@enduml
